column2: Eames Premium Replica Management Office Chair
column4: Inspired by the popular Eames creation, this replica is made of fine materials to do the original justice. It features fine leather on the front, with a high quality polyurethane to match the leather used on the reverse.

Break from convention and make your office feel more inviting to you, starting with this gorgeous chair. This velvet office chair with brass-coloured base injects a glam touch to your serious space, the padding and adjustable seat height provides comfort, and the castors make moving to your filing cabinet a breeze.

Consider luxurious touches in your office, starting with seating, for a space refresh. This chic, modern-inspired chair is upholstered with velvet, and the brass-coloured metal frame lends minimalist style to the piece. It's complete with castors, and a gas lift for adjustable height for your comfort.

column2: Tan Kinsey Faux Leather Office Chair
column4:
With the appearance and feel similar to a genuine leather, faux leather chairs like this Kinsey office chair is the real deal.

Combining functionality, affordability and style, it could be a great option when building your home office.

column2: Eames Premium Replica High Back Soft Pad Management Office Chair
column4: This fun, modern design is a popular Eames creation. The replica is made of fine materials to do the original justice. The thick cushions offer comfortable support so you can linger awhile at the office.
